						               													<description>In this Japanese legendary tale, you and your friends must work together in building up your party, while journeying towards the place where the demons resides.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If players are able to defeat all the demons, they will be victorious.  If they are unable to do so, and the demons get the upper hand, the demons will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play:  There are 2 main phases:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Exploration phase: &amp;#10;The starting player rolls the dice, and each player moves their character the number of spaces of the dice.  Reveal the token that you land on and resolve its effect.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The demon battle: &amp;#10;Once players reach the area where the demons resides, the battle will begin.  Players choose the character they wish to fight with. Taking turns, each player attempt to battle the demon using their abilities (and sometimes dice), if they are successful they can fight the next demon.  If they are unsuccessful, the next player can attempt to defeat that demon.  Once all the demons are defeated the players win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
